{
  "stem": "16313.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got a piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it is good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this story ended with this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- then-- then I was going again, some places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I go north, some places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From this place I go north.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was something in--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All kind of-- all kind of people, what they just run away from-- oh.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All kind of--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a special person.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody look for him-- for himself in this situation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody must be from them self because you can't depend on nobody in these kind of situations.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Girls?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Girls was-- I'll tell you about the gross.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Happened to me when I was in some places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was in some places like this, like a prisoner in some places.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't remember these places and all kind of place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I go back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went back to the Polish Army because they start to form another Polish Army, Buzuluk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I went over there to the Buzuluk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they start to form an army, Polish Army because they got a special treaty with the Polish government in London to make a new Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this Polish Army, under General Anders, supposed to fight, again, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I went to the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was-- I met my-- a friend of mine's.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "God forbid too, was over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In this-- in this compound-- in this-- in this whole compound, what that's supposed to make the armies, start a big epidemic of typhus, black typhus.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was one of the victims.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The army go away to Persia, to Persia, to Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was left around, like me, a lot of people what that--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Israel.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Army, again, are Anders'.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, they give them a chance to go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
